#. type: Plain text
#: /home/h-kuroki/work/drbd-doc-ja/proto/v9/base/adoc/linstor-introduction.adoc:307
msgid "The resource group that the resource definition belongs to"
msgstr "リソース定義が所属するリソースグループ"

#. type: Plain text
