msgid ""
"The TCP port to use for the resource's connection, for example, when DRBD is "
"replicating data"
msgstr ""
"リソースの接続に使用するTCPポートは、たとえば、DRBDがデータをレプリケートして"
"いる場合に使用されます。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/h-kuroki/work/drbd-doc-ja/proto/v9/base/adoc/linstor-introduction.adoc:310
msgid ""
"Other attributes such as a resource's storage layers, peer slots, and "
